snippet.title: Battlefield 1 Gameplay Series: Weapons
snippet.description:
From shotguns to bayonets and gas grenades, find out about the Weapons of Battlefield 1. 

Battlefield 1 will be available from Oct 21st 2016 on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC.

See all the featurettes: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLLpjKzWIuEfnbUB3CbQoYM-eNFHVXABP0

Don't miss the next video in the BF1 gameplay series: http://bit.ly/270eMcA
